    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/67d37eb3573795175e62c36201e80ade.avif?t=1740740575\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras_big/67d37eb3573795175e62c36201e80ade.avif?t=1740740575 width=800 height=290 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ogora: Prologue is the free version of the roguelike deckbuilding game<strong> Ogora.</strong> Get a taste of the ever winding world of Ogora: Prologue as Jax, the trusty battle axe who will hack and slash (with a few wary friends by his side).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this prologue you will be able to find a limited selection of partners, cards, trinkets and monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/82fc018c3e4dd94760127a95c939161e.avif?t=1740740575\" width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/2115e93f256e0b11ad7631da43a99d1b.poster.avif?t=1740740575\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/2115e93f256e0b11ad7631da43a99d1b.webm?t=1740740575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/2115e93f256e0b11ad7631da43a99d1b.mp4?t=1740740575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the magical garden of Ogora and test your mind (and your luck) against your enchanted friends - while the Wizard tries to get a moment of peace!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover secrets within the hedges of the garden (or make a path of your own!). But be careful, not everyone in the garden will aid you!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/87c9664d483c3ae674c541576638abe8.avif?t=1740740575\" width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/9c74528650f0941e8e1070773548ccd2.poster.avif?t=1740740575\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/9c74528650f0941e8e1070773548ccd2.webm?t=1740740575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/9c74528650f0941e8e1070773548ccd2.mp4?t=1740740575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draft new powers, ancient spells, or hoard your explosives for those pesky pillows and ornery ottomans that block your path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with a massive number of unique cards, heavily guarded spells, and hidden trinkets – seriously, some of these are pretty secret.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run will present new challenges, difficult choices, and a unique friend to help you!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/356e6a7c50bbb2a9cd231c9b02313392.avif?t=1740740575\" width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/5ef69d55f47652fd9fbac9da5c66aa08.poster.avif?t=1740740575\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/5ef69d55f47652fd9fbac9da5c66aa08.webm?t=1740740575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265260/extras/5ef69d55f47652fd9fbac9da5c66aa08.mp4?t=1740740575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select your hero and choose a Partner to aid you in your journey. Each partner offers unique powers and abilities, so choose carefully!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whoever you don’t choose is out to win, so make sure you’re prepared!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your own path as you journey through - Ogora!</p>",
